title: [Gyldemar Forest, The Barrens]
description: Splinters of wood, now blackened, lie like fallen pine needles throughout the area.  Only a single stump interrupts the field of blasted wood.
Splinters of wood, now blackened, lie like fallen pine needles throughout the area.  Only a single stump interrupts the field of blasted wood, a dangerous obstacle in the black of the night.
